## n8n@0.197.0 View the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.196.0...n8n@0.197.0) for this version.
**Release date:** 2022-10-10 This release includes six new nodes, focused around infrastructure management. It also adds support for drag and drop data mapping in the JSON input view, and includes bug fixes.
